{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":833,"text":"We need to change the culture\nin our jails and prisons,"},{"time":5013,"text":"especially for young inmates."},{"time":7520,"text":"New York state is one\nof only two in the U.S."},{"time":9842,"text":"that automatically arrests and tries\n16- to 17-year-olds as adults."},{"time":14950,"text":"This culture of violence\ntakes these young people"},{"time":17297,"text":"and puts them in a hostile environment,"},{"time":19339,"text":"and the correctional officers pretty much\nallow any and everything to go on."},{"time":23381,"text":"There's not really much\nfor these young people to do"},{"time":26188,"text":"to actually enhance their talent\nand actually rehabilitate them."},{"time":31038,"text":"Until we can raise the age\nof criminal responsibility to 18,"},{"time":34284,"text":"we need to focus on changing\nthe daily lives of these young people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38155,"text":"I know firsthand."},{"time":40329,"text":"Before I ever turned 18,"},{"time":41908,"text":"I spent approximately\n400 days on Rikers Island,"},{"time":45855,"text":"and to add to that"},{"time":47109,"text":"I spent almost 300 days\nin solitary confinement,"},{"time":50963,"text":"and let me tell you this:"},{"time":53680,"text":"Screaming at the top of your lungs\nall day on your cell door"},{"time":56768,"text":"or screaming at the top\nof your lungs out the window,"},{"time":59345,"text":"it gets tiring."},{"time":61267,"text":"Since there's not much for you to do\nwhile you're in there,"},{"time":64064,"text":"you start pacing\nback and forth in your cell,"},{"time":66347,"text":"you start talking to yourself,"},{"time":68483,"text":"your thoughts start running wild,"},{"time":70480,"text":"and then your thoughts\nbecome your own worst enemy."},{"time":73963,"text":"Jails are actually supposed\nto rehabilitate a person,"},{"time":76958,"text":"not cause him or her\nto become more angry,"},{"time":79651,"text":"frustrated, and feel more hopeless."},{"time":82391,"text":"Since there's not a discharge plan\nput in place for these young people,"},{"time":86294,"text":"they pretty much \nreenter society with nothing."},{"time":91168,"text":"And there's not really much for them to do\nto keep them from recidivating."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95823,"text":"But it all starts with the C.O.s."},{"time":98545,"text":"It's very easy for some people"},{"time":100513,"text":"to look at these correctional officers\nas the good guys"},{"time":103207,"text":"and the inmates as the bad guys,"},{"time":105482,"text":"or vice versa for some,"},{"time":107178,"text":"but it's a little more than that."},{"time":108849,"text":"See, these C.O.s are normal,\neveryday people."},{"time":111844,"text":"They come from the same neighborhoods\nas the population they \"serve.\""},{"time":117725,"text":"They're just normal people."},{"time":119597,"text":"They're not robots, and there's \nnothing special about them."},{"time":123261,"text":"They do pretty much everything\nanybody else in society does."},{"time":127023,"text":"The male C.O.s want to talk\nand flirt with the female C.O.s."},{"time":130922,"text":"They play the little high school\nkid games with each other."},{"time":133731,"text":"They politic with one another."},{"time":135635,"text":"And the female C.O.s gossip to each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139954,"text":"So I spent numerous amounts of time\nwith numerous amounts of C.O.s,"},{"time":145944,"text":"and let me tell you about\nthis one in particular named Monroe."},{"time":148856,"text":"One day he pulled me\nin between the A and B doors"},{"time":151354,"text":"which separate the north\nand south sides of our housing unit."},{"time":154673,"text":"He pulled me there because I had\na physical altercation"},{"time":157270,"text":"with another young man in my housing unit,"},{"time":159290,"text":"and he felt, since there was\na female officer working on the floor,"},{"time":162773,"text":"that I violated his shift."},{"time":165258,"text":"So he punched me in my chest."},{"time":167255,"text":"He kind of knocked the wind out of me."},{"time":169391,"text":"I wasn't impulsive,\nI didn't react right away,"},{"time":172248,"text":"because I know this is their house."},{"time":174896,"text":"I have no wins."},{"time":176746,"text":"All he has to do is pull his pin\nand backup will come immediately."},{"time":183084,"text":"So I just gave him a look in his eyes"},{"time":185645,"text":"and I guess he saw the anger\nand frustration just burning,"},{"time":188904,"text":"and he said to me,"},{"time":190869,"text":"\"Your eyes are going to get you\nin a lot of trouble,"},{"time":193331,"text":"because you're looking\nlike you want to fight.\""},{"time":195837,"text":"So he commenced\nto taking off his utility belt,"},{"time":198206,"text":"he took off his shirt and his badge,"},{"time":200297,"text":"and he said, \"We could fight.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":202334,"text":"So I asked him, \"You gonna hold it down?\""},{"time":205151,"text":"Now, that's a term that's\ncommonly used on Rikers Island"},{"time":208064,"text":"meaning that you're not\ngoing to say anything to anybody,"},{"time":210731,"text":"and you're not going to report it."},{"time":212958,"text":"He said, \"Yeah, I'm gonna hold it down.\nYou gonna hold it down?\""},{"time":216735,"text":"I didn't even respond."},{"time":218406,"text":"I just punched him right in his face,"},{"time":220331,"text":"and we began fighting\nright then and there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223027,"text":"Towards the end of the fight,\nhe slammed me up against the wall,"},{"time":227347,"text":"so while we were tussled up,\nhe said to me, \"You good?\""},{"time":230852,"text":"as if he got the best of me,"},{"time":232617,"text":"but in my mind, I know\nI got the best of him,"},{"time":235241,"text":"so I replied very cocky,"},{"time":237244,"text":"\"Oh, I'm good, you good?\""},{"time":239372,"text":"He said, \"Yeah, I'm good, \nI'm good.\""},{"time":241366,"text":"We let go, he shook my hand,\nsaid he gave me my respect,"},{"time":245532,"text":"gave me a cigarette and sent me on my way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249723,"text":"Believe it or not, you come across\nsome C.O.s on Rikers Island"},{"time":253464,"text":"that'll fight you one-on-one."},{"time":256040,"text":"They feel that they understand how it is,"},{"time":258247,"text":"and they feel that I'm going\nto meet you where you're at."},{"time":261055,"text":"Since this is how you commonly\nhandle your disputes,"},{"time":263551,"text":"we can handle it in that manner."},{"time":265630,"text":"I walk away from it like a man,\nyou walk away from it like a man,"},{"time":268904,"text":"and that's it."},{"time":270325,"text":"Some C.O.s feel that\nthey're jailing with you."},{"time":272477,"text":"This is why they have that mentality\nand that attitude"},{"time":275047,"text":"and they go by that concept."},{"time":277078,"text":"In some instances, we're in it\ntogether with the C.O.s."},{"time":280543,"text":"However, institutions need to give\nthese correctional officers"},{"time":283617,"text":"proper trainings on how to properly deal\nwith the adolescent population,"},{"time":286995,"text":"and they also need\nto give them proper trainings"},{"time":289240,"text":"on how to deal with \nthe mental health population as well."},{"time":292777,"text":"These C.O.s play a big factor\nin these young people's lives"},{"time":296086,"text":"for x amount of time until a disposition\nis reached on their case."},{"time":299444,"text":"So why not try to mentor\nthese young people while they're there?"},{"time":304101,"text":"Why not try to give them some type\nof insight to make a change,"},{"time":308322,"text":"so once they reenter back into society,"},{"time":311783,"text":"they're doing something positive?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":316217,"text":"A second big thing to help our teens\nin jails is better programming."},{"time":321626,"text":"When I was on Rikers Island,\nthe huge thing was solitary confinement."},{"time":325644,"text":"Solitary confinement\nwas originally designed"},{"time":328373,"text":"to break a person mentally,\nphysically and emotionally."},{"time":332065,"text":"That's what it was designed for."},{"time":335756,"text":"The U.S. Attorney General\nrecently released a report"},{"time":338224,"text":"stating that they're going\nto ban solitary confinement"},{"time":340749,"text":"in New York state for teens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":343698,"text":"One thing that kept me sane while I\nwas in solitary confinement was reading."},{"time":347900,"text":"I tried to educate myself\nas much as possible."},{"time":350802,"text":"I read any and everything\nI could get my hands on."},{"time":353427,"text":"And aside from that,\nI wrote music and short stories."},{"time":357118,"text":"Some programs that I feel\nwould benefit our young people"},{"time":362194,"text":"are art therapy programs"},{"time":365245,"text":"for the kids that like to draw\nand have that talent,"},{"time":368310,"text":"and what about the young individuals\nthat are musically inclined?"},{"time":372252,"text":"How about a music program for them\nthat actually teaches them"},{"time":375139,"text":"how to write and make music?"},{"time":377536,"text":"Just a thought."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378960,"text":"When adolescents come to Rikers Island,"},{"time":381029,"text":"C74, RNDC is the building\nthat they're housed in."},{"time":385143,"text":"That's nicknamed \"gladiator school,\""},{"time":388704,"text":"because you have a young individual\ncoming in from the street"},{"time":391586,"text":"thinking that they're tough,"},{"time":393363,"text":"being surrounded by a bunch\nof other young individuals"},{"time":396683,"text":"from all of the five boroughs,\nand everybody feels that they're tough."},{"time":400327,"text":"So now you have a bunch of young gentlemen\npoking their chests out"},{"time":404322,"text":"feeling that I have to prove\nI'm equally as tough as you"},{"time":407712,"text":"or I'm tougher than you, you and you."},{"time":410146,"text":"But let's be honest:"},{"time":411734,"text":"That culture is very dangerous\nand damaging to our young people."},{"time":416625,"text":"We need to help institutions\nand these teens realize"},{"time":419579,"text":"that they don't have to lead\nthe previous lifestyle that they led"},{"time":422874,"text":"when they were on the street,\nthat they can actually make a change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426311,"text":"It's sad to report\nthat while I was in prison,"},{"time":429762,"text":"I used to hear dudes talking about\nwhen they get released from prison,"},{"time":433991,"text":"what type of crimes\nthey're going to commit"},{"time":437079,"text":"when they get back in the street."},{"time":439703,"text":"The conversations used to sound\nsomething like this:"},{"time":443616,"text":"\"Oh, when I hit the street,\nmy brother got this connection"},{"time":446443,"text":"for this, that and the third,\""},{"time":447891,"text":"or, \"My man over here\ngot this connection for the low price."},{"time":450735,"text":"Let's exchange information,\""},{"time":452142,"text":"and, \"When we hit the town,\nwe're going to do it real big.\""},{"time":454925,"text":"I used to hear these conversations\nand think to myself, \"Wow,"},{"time":457784,"text":"these dudes are really talking about\ngoing back in the street"},{"time":460716,"text":"and committing future crimes.\""},{"time":462248,"text":"So I came up with a name for that:"},{"time":463990,"text":"I called it a go-back-to-jail-quick scheme"},{"time":466939,"text":"because really, how long\nis that going to last?"},{"time":470523,"text":"You get a retirement plan with that?"},{"time":472883,"text":"Nice little pension? 401(k)? 403(b)?"},{"time":476341,"text":"You get health insurance? Dental?"},{"time":479639,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":481568,"text":"But I will tell you this:"},{"time":483424,"text":"Being in jail and being in prison,"},{"time":485166,"text":"I came across some of the most\nintelligent, brilliant,"},{"time":488788,"text":"and talented people\nthat I would ever meet."},{"time":491574,"text":"I've seen individuals\ntake a potato chip bag"},{"time":493803,"text":"and turn it into the most\nbeautiful picture frame."},{"time":496434,"text":"I've seen individuals take\nthe state soap that's provided for free"},{"time":499546,"text":"and turn them into\nthe most beautiful sculptures"},{"time":501925,"text":"that would make Michelangelo\nlook like a kindergartner made it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506217,"text":"At the age of 21, I was in\na maximum-security prison"},{"time":509304,"text":"called Elmira Correctional Facility."},{"time":511107,"text":"I just came out of the weight shack\nfrom working out,"},{"time":513615,"text":"and I saw an older gentleman that I knew\nstanding in the middle of the yard"},{"time":517148,"text":"just looking up at the sky."},{"time":518453,"text":"Mind you, this older gentlemen was serving\na 33-and-a-third-to-life sentence"},{"time":522649,"text":"in which he already had served\n20 years of that sentence.\n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":526081,"text":"So I walk up to him and I said,"},{"time":527895,"text":"\"O.G., what's going on, man, you good?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":529857,"text":"He looked at me, and he said,\n\"Yeah, I'm good, young blood.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":532708,"text":"I'm like, \"So what are you looking\nup at the sky for, man?"},{"time":535441,"text":"What's so fascinating up there?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":537139,"text":"He said, \"You look up\nand you tell me what you see.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":541087,"text":"\"Clouds.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":544615,"text":"He said, \"All right.\nWhat else do you see?\""},{"time":547522,"text":"At that time, it was a plane passing by."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550023,"text":"I said, \"All right, I see an airplane.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":552050,"text":"He said, \"Exactly, and what's \non that airplane?\" \"People.\""},{"time":556206,"text":"\"Exactly. Now where's that plane\nand those people going?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":560083,"text":"\"I don't know. You know?"},{"time":561569,"text":"Please let me know if you do.\nThen let me get some lottery numbers.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":566236,"text":"He said, \"You're missing\nthe big picture, young blood."},{"time":569394,"text":"That plane with those people\nis going somewhere,"},{"time":571739,"text":"while we're here stuck."},{"time":574317,"text":"The big picture is this:"},{"time":576151,"text":"That plane with those people\ngoing somewhere,"},{"time":578519,"text":"that's life passing us by\nwhile we behind these walls, stuck.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":586252,"text":"Ever since that day,"},{"time":588318,"text":"that sparked something in my mind\nand made me know I had to make a change."},{"time":592497,"text":"Growing up, I was always\na good, smart kid."},{"time":595794,"text":"Some people would say\nI was a little too smart for my own good."},{"time":600743,"text":"I had dreams of becoming\nan architect or an archaeologist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":606290,"text":"Currently, I'm working\nat the Fortune Society,"},{"time":608473,"text":"which is a reentry program,"},{"time":610222,"text":"and I work with people as a case manager\nthat are at high risk for recidivism."},{"time":614765,"text":"So I connect them\nwith the services that they need"},{"time":617171,"text":"once they're released from jail and prison"},{"time":619200,"text":"so they can make a positive transition\nback into society."},{"time":622326,"text":"If I was to see my 15-year-old self today,"},{"time":625121,"text":"I would sit down and talk to him\nand try to educate him"},{"time":628092,"text":"and I would let him know,\n\"Listen, this is me. I'm you."},{"time":632037,"text":"This is us. We are one."},{"time":634431,"text":"Everything that you're about to do,\nI know what you're gonna do"},{"time":637473,"text":"before you do it because I already did it,"},{"time":640097,"text":"and I would encourage him\nnot to hang out with x, y and z people."},{"time":643734,"text":"I would tell him not to be\nin such-and-such place."},{"time":646540,"text":"I would tell him,\nkeep your behind in school, man,"},{"time":648916,"text":"because that's where you need to be,"},{"time":650836,"text":"because that's what's going\nto get you somewhere in life."},{"time":653540,"text":"This is the message\nthat we should be sharing"},{"time":655703,"text":"with our young men and young women."},{"time":657576,"text":"We shouldn't be treating them as adults\nand putting them in cultures of violence"},{"time":661504,"text":"that are nearly impossible\nfor them to escape."}]},{"cues":[{"time":664203,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":666268,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}